com.facebook.rendercore

Interface Node.LayoutResult<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    InternalNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultInternalNode, MeasureResult
    Enclosing interface:
    Node<RenderContext>

    public static interface Node.LayoutResult<T>
    Represents the result of a Layout pass. A LayoutResult has a reference to its originating Node and all the layout information needed to position the content of such Node.
